# .npmrc — committed file with portable defaults.
#
# Per-machine overrides (e.g. routing the pnpm content-addressable
# store to an external SSD to avoid root-volume OOM) live in `.npmrc.local`
# which is gitignored. pnpm reads `.npmrc.local` automatically (newer
# pnpm) OR you can `cat .npmrc.local >> .npmrc` AFTER cloning if your
# pnpm version doesn't.
#
# Example .npmrc.local for the LEXAR-routed setup (Eva's machine):
#   store-dir=/Volumes/LEXAR/Smarter-Claw-v1port/pnpm-store
#
# CI runners get the default ~/.local/share/pnpm/store path, which
# works on the standard Ubuntu image.
